Package: libretranslate-gui
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1
Maintainer: Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>
Homepage: https://github.com/yeager/libretranslate-gui
Description: GTK4/Adwaita translation assistant using LibreTranslate API
 A desktop application for translating text using the LibreTranslate API.
 Supports live translation, batch mode, .po/.ts file translation suggestions,
 configurable server URL, translation history, and clipboard integration.
